Package: RMSTSS
Type: Package
Title: Sample Size Calculation Using RMST for Survival Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Arnab", family = "Aich", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           email = "arnab.aich99@gmail.com", 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-7801-6701"))
Description: This package provides functions for estimating model parameters and
    calculating statistical power and sample size for tests related to Restricted
    Mean Survival Time (RMST) and dynamic prediction models. It includes utilities
    for simulating survival and treatment data for power analysis.
